Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 心情也变得超级恬静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么十分在意的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？阿鲁？我既没有在想阿鲁也没有在意阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}注：日语「有吗」与「阿鲁」发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么都没在想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级纯情少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 送走炎热的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯渐渐染上了秋天的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是爱丽丝成为正式领航员之后的第一个营业日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 在开始共同练习之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华提议去看看她的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.41,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那份 赏月之夜的心动…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领航员小姐又很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 那是叹息桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}Ponte dei Sospiri：叹息桥建于1603年 因桥上死囚的\N叹息声而得名 据说恋人们在桥下接吻就可以天长地久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:03:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 导游手册上写着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在正在前往的 就是叹息桥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美得让人叹息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 名字的由来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在地球的杜卡雷宫接受了判决的死囚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}杜卡雷宫：古代威尼斯共和国总督的政厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在经过这座桥的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会深深叹一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这次来对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她怎么这么紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来浑身僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们一定还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢二位的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来客人是很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 请忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被爱丽丝发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级注意到了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我们偶然路过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 偶然看到了爱丽丝的工作情形…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来二位刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我的工作啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…你看 不是还算可以的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 倒划着去追踪猫咪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还完美地继承了雅典娜前辈的周到服务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从那里就开始看了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷看超级禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…那之外就完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位想说什么就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像玩具机器人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀僵硬得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间让你沮丧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你已经是正式领航员啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚去赏月如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏月？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天天气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮一定很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏月…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 还是第一次赏月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在AQUA没有这种习俗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在赏月的时候要有团子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是模仿地球的月亮做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就吃了两个 你好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就吃四个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁…禁止吃着碗里的想着锅里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈你超级律人不律己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆不隆咚的肚子～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长圆不隆咚的肚子可不是月见团子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是邮递员大叔推荐给我的黑米茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节喝热饮真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 阿鲁好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 为什么阿鲁他要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们三个人赏月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说起和星球有关的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就得叫阿鲁来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会告诉我们很多事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为上次看流星雨小后辈你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才特地叫阿鲁过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他八成又是在加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能迷路了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华前辈 超级可爱的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你今天邀我赏月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看着月亮 我感觉轻松了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 我感觉能像月亮一样圆满地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好地完成自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 再来一杯茶如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？嘛社长不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我加班做得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 工作狂禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀…真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不过多亏我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能独占这深夜的幽静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华小姐 危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么是阿鲁你道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我太重了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好城里的井都是已经废弃了的枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不至于淹死…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是麻烦了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在还未启用水道之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个广场都设置了井口收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用以解决生活用水问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早晚这里都挤满了来打水的夫人们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如人们说的 是井边会议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小后辈带来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长你在听我说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把·小·后·辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带·过·来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你也跟着跳下来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上去把小后辈叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又跑回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说嘛社长啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 嘛社长还是猫baby啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 嘛社长是能够理解人类语言的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的水星猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会！把小后辈…叫来…的…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在我们全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是那样 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应不应该抱着期待呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点悬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果变成诡异的赏月了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮为什么会绕着AQUA转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为相互吸引的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与相互远离的力量同时作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我说过的相互吸引的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和圆周运动产生的离心力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成了微妙的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 月亮既无法靠近 也无法远离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕着AQUA在转动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像某人一样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外侧的月亮被利用于宇宙空间站等等领域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在真空中完成的科学实验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矿物资源的开采
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的月亮上的陨石坑被比喻为各种形状哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如有着巨螯的螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在编织的老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子 女性的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿饼的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到兔子我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙空间站的兔子薄饼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那个很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想吃吃看 前些天就邮购了一些来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说还会附赠赞美月亮的明信片套装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之那种的全部禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井底下还真黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你怕黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力调节员一般都是在黑漆漆的地方工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛在晚上也能看清东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时虽然阳光无法进入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过地下世界的照明设备非常齐全…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁君不用怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 有大姐姐陪着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮变成两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内侧的月亮体积大概是外侧月亮的1.8倍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在AQUA的静止轨道内转动着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8小时以内就能绕着AQUA转动一周的内侧月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在AQUA上空5900公里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个非常近的轨道内转动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个距离跟地球与月球的距离比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有其65分之1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过接近的小小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了太多AQUA的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久 一定会粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到AQUA影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有月亮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对AQUA来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最最接近不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被月亮影响着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费掉了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝…蓝华小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费掉什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 还好找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你居然掉到那里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是对救命恩人说的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感谢过嘛社长了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从「浪费掉了啦」那个时候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 浪费掉什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产…产生离心力的方法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果害怕靠近而犹豫不前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子就会饿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是产生引力的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 什么东西让人害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿鲁的大叔用语让人害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 什么东西浪费掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}你是明知故问对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 虽然这是心血来潮的赏月大会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家都找回了平时的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就变成了一个非常开心的秋夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里姐姐 月亮除了有引力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还拥有别的美好的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年秋天我也想参加赏月大会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在激情燃烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小后辈一样～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝很有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.81,0:24:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些 瞬息万变的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:10.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:20.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:30.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:41.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:46.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:53.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:02:00.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:10.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.52,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:24.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:32.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:37.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:10.22,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:20.21,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:30.34,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.74,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:41.47,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:46.19,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:53.31,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:02:00.25,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 崭露头角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.61,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远地 充满
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:10.25,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让人陶醉的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.52,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:24.24,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}每个温暖的 日子往复着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:32.66,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不经意间 从那远方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:37.36,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:40.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}金の波 岸辺に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:46.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}あこがれ目覚めるの 朝に
